data.text: As far as I remember and think back, I can't remember I've ever been or heard about any regulations whatsoever about which clothes you can wear, and which clothes you cannot. However, I still think that ... everybody thinks about, most people at least think about what clothes would not be the thing to wear today for class and et cetera, but no, not in terms of regulations, not in terms of any rules no. But do you think there should be rules, so should it be more like decide yourself?
